age(senderId, dto)`：事务内插入消息、校验权限、返回消息记录。\n   105\t  - `veri
fyConversationMembership(userId, conversationId)`：查询 `conversation_participan
ts`。\n   106\t\n   107\t---\n   108\t\n   109\t### Step 2：后端已读回执与会话列
